    <title>Typescript errors when using `npx frontity create --typescript`</title>
    <link>https://community.frontity.org/t/typescript-errors-when-using-npx-frontity-create-typescript/5549</link>
    <description>I am starting yet another project, and this time we want to use TS. We decided to use the mars-typescript-theme as a start to save us some time.

So after I run `npx frontity create --typescript` everything seems to work properly, but then I am getting ts warning/error in the frontity.settings.ts file.

I am very new to TS so I am really struggling to figure out what is going on.

Here are some screenshots of what i see in VSC:

![Screenshot 2021-12-08 at 14.57.14|690x160](upload://ifuImr7uC4i3oR9GD2n53JCw9AJ.png)

![Screenshot 2021-12-08 at 14.57.27|690x107](upload://iT2fhsSoDzR4WriUbgNdTB3lEvj.png)

![Screenshot 2021-12-08 at 14.57.36|690x161](upload://fI8ijjkFucluRuubJkWcrONjcdR.png)


For testing purposes I also made a new sandbox from that repository, and weird enough there i dont get this warnings. 

https://codesandbox.io/s/kind-resonance-octou?file=/frontity.settings.ts

Could this be an issue with my VSC? I am really confused. 
Hopefully someone can help with this.</description>
